msgid "Unconcerned Punk"
msgstr "Matón Despreocupado"

msgctxt "84_Unconcerned Punk"
msgid "Wait, was that Majima-san? You hear his name all over town,\\r\n"
"but I've never actually seen the guy before."
msgstr "Espera, ¿era ese Majima-san? Escuchas su nombre por toda la ciudad,\\r\n"
"pero nunca he visto al tipo antes."

msgctxt "96_Unconcerned Punk"
msgid "Looks like a real piece of work. Little shitboy like me'll never compare to a top dog like that."
msgstr ""

